2007-04-27 18:22  erk

	* RTIA/main.cc: Suicide is not the way to go :)) You should NEVER
	  send yourself SIGKILL In this case the process will terminate
	  after receiving SIGALARM because the SIGALARM will break
	  execute() statement and let the RTIA process terminate.

